{"tid":2296651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有片 侯夫喺澳門格蘭披治大賽車上台攞獎時疑似舉五一手勢 賽後被判接觸違規被罰30秒失冠","createTime":"2020-11-22T16:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T17:30:10.000Z","uid":121021,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e5512882ce688a3268a3ddcd190245ad1fb26b1c","tid":2296651,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cNd8sJGJsS4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcNd8sJGJsS4&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=15a64b88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cNd8sJGJsS4</a><br />\n<br />\n澳門格蘭披治大賽車周日上演各項賽事正賽，焦點賽事之一東望洋大賽現連番意外，中國車手楊曦在文華東方彎失控後，吳怡帆收掣不及高速撞上，共12圈的賽事在六圈後腰斬，實際鬥車不足兩圈下，侯夫（Rob Huff）本來有望第11度於東望洋賽道贏車，但他賽後與香港車手甄卓偉雙雙被罰。<br />\n賽會其後判罰侯夫在與馬青驊的接觸屬違規，罰加30秒，失去冠軍資格；本獲季軍的甄卓偉則被指在黃旗下沒有減速而同樣被罰加30秒。最終排名為中國車手張志強奪冠，兩位香港車手王日昇及盧思豪分別得亞、季軍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201122/RA726SG4VZBY7FSZ3XP6CCCXPI/?fbclid=IwAR1U5gR836Rwi5eaIJs6laXUC1KD7jTpFaM6Hcvw3f2_OB6BZuLAYF1VOQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201122%2FRA726SG4VZBY7FSZ3XP6CCCXPI%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1U5gR836Rwi5eaIJs6laXUC1KD7jTpFaM6Hcvw3f2_OB6BZuLAYF1VOQc&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=10ad9e32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20201122%2FRA726SG4VZBY7FSZ3XP6CCCXPI%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1U5gR836Rwi5eaIJs6laXUC1KD7jTpFaM6Hcvw3f2_OB6BZuLAYF1VOQc&h=6b337a04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20201122/RA726SG4VZBY7FSZ3XP6CCCXPI/?fbclid=IwAR1U5gR836Rwi5eaIJs6laXUC1KD7jTpFaM6Hcvw3f2_OB6BZuLAYF1VOQc</a>"},{"pid":"1bda7bb5a288c82360b36eb58d8e3be77ab819ff","tid":2296651,"uid":121021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji